        "content": "<p><code>calc</code> is definitely not intended for single line computation. Why don’t you simply write</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- first part of the exercise</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">left</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">addarith</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">h3</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">right</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">addarith</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">h4</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
